berna Recreo Espartinas', ''),('atocha hotel madrid tapestry collection by hilton', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Atocha Hotel Madrid, Tapestry Collection by Hilton', 'Another favorite, understated hotel in Madrid. There is no pool, and it isn''t one of the high end Hilton chains. The staff are incredibly nice, the rooms are well laid out & stylish, and it''s conveniently located.'),('hotel indigo madrid princesa an ihg hotel', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Hotel Indigo Madrid - Princesa, an IHG Hotel', 'Often a very affordable place to stay in a quiet neighborhood. The hotel is not the "sexiest" but is high quality, affordable, and conveniently located.'),('mandarosso', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Mandarosso', ''),('es vietnam restaurante', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Es Vietnam Restaurante', ''),('cuatro gatos cerveceria', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Cuatro Gatos Cerveceria', 'Fun vibes, good variety of different beers on tap and bottled, cool music on playlist. Very low key. Good place to end the evening.'),('museo nacional centro de arte reina sofia', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Museo Nacional Centro de Arte Reina Sofía', 'If you go to one art museum... see this one. Don''t just go to the Prado, do both... seriously. Guernica is much more stunning in person than in pictures and really makes you FEEL the depth of the Spanish civil war.'),('embarcadero de el retiro', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Embarcadero de El Retiro', 'Bring someone cool and RIDE THE BOATS!!!'),('motteau pasteleria', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Motteau Pasteleria', 'AMAZING -> might be the best bakery I''ve ever visited in the world.'),('restaurante cocteleria inclan brutal bar', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Restaurante-Coctelería Inclán Brutal Bar', ''),('restaurante rosi la loca', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Restaurante Rosi La Loca', ''),('nigiri moncloa', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Nigiri Moncloa', 'Quick, it''s not the most amazing but prices are right.'),('nigiri plaza de espana', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Nigiri Plaza de España', 'Takeaway sushi, not bad, decent prices. Great choice if you’re in a hurry in the neighborhood'),('la morocha madrid', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'La Morocha Madrid', ''),('cevicheria rokoto la latina', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Cevicheria ROKOTO La Latina', ''),('mercado de la cebada', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Mercado de la Cebada', 'Much better market than San Miguel. Better food, better prices, more authentic.'),('che birra cerveceria argentina', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Che!!! Birra!!! - Cervecería Argentina', ''),('st mary royal of the almudena', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'St Mary Royal of the Almudena', 'Cool mainly because it has a crypt to see'),('madrid cablecar rosales station', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Madrid Cablecar • Rosales Station', 'The best way to get to the zoo! The views are breathtaking and occasionally they stop the cable system so you can sit and take in the park views.'),('falafeleria', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Falafeleria', 'Amazing falafel'),('mercado de san fernando', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Mercado de San Fernando', 'Alot more "authentic" than the other mercado a few minutes away. Hours are weird and I believe it''s not open as late as google says. Go early in the AM, walk around and have a beer.'),('aloft madrid gran via', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Aloft Madrid Gran Via', 'Fav place to stay in Madrid. The rooftop bar/ pool is open to non guests, the staff that work there are super nice, the views are incredible. Go for sunset!'),('el corte ingles', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'El Corte Inglés', 'Go for the "gourmet experience" on the top floor (that is where el camino sacramento is). I love coming here for sunset. Amazing views of the red roofs and the prices are high for madrid but reasonable.'),('zoo aquarium de madrid', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Zoo Aquarium de Madrid', 'They have pandas :)'),('palacio de cristal', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Palacio de Cristal', 'rotating art installation. it''s free to go to so even 