Prices are 3-4x what you will expect to spend elsewhere, it''s a cool place to go and see the wrought iron structure and glass paneling. Beware of the beggars around... they''re a pain...'),('restaurante amicis', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Restaurante Amicis', 'Get a reservation, you can almost never just walk in. Lovely quaint little place with an amazing menu that is updated all the time. Good for a group'),('tiki taco santa isabel', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Tiki Taco Santa Isabel', 'Fun taco place. Only go if you’re around'),('brew wild pizza bar', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'BREW WILD PIZZA BAR', 'Amazing selection of craft beers. Have the truffle eggplant pizza'),('yatai market', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Yatai Market', 'Asian food, expensive for Madrid, but everyone can eat what they want'),('citynizer plaza', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Citynizer Plaza', 'Sweet outdoor plaza place to hang, go if the weather is good'),('camino sacramento', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Camino Sacramento', 'Amazing steaks… 75% of the time.. cheap, gourmet food around. Depends on the cook but prices are reasonable.'),('churreria santa ana', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Churrería Santa Ana', 'Hole in the wall. “Dive bar churros”'),('nina pasta bar', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Nina Pasta Bar', 'No longer opened, the owner/chef passed away unexpectedly. I keep on this list because this might have been the best pasta restaurant in the world. Pour one out.'),('la puerta amarilla steaks burgers', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'La Puerta Amarilla (steaks & burgers)', ''),('los desamparados', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Los Desamparados', ''),('kausa madrid by gonzales bastidas', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Kausa Madrid by Gonzáles Bastidas', ''),('el cogollo de la descarga', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'El cogollo de la descarga', ''),('el sur', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'El Sur', ''),('fabrica maravillas', ARRAY['madrid']::text[], 'Fábrica Maravillas', 'Unpretentious craft brewery with a nice variety of taps.